videos.headline: New Mexico WR goes up to grab TD
videos.description: New Mexico's Tevaka Tuioti hits Delane Hart-Johnson on a slant for an 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Wisconsin WR makes stellar one-handed catch
videos.description: A.J. Taylor secures a one-handed catch down the sideline for a 28-yard gain vs. New Mexico.

videos.headline: Taylor loses fumble in red zone
videos.description: Wisconsin running back Jonathan Taylor coughs up the ball inside the 10 and New Mexico recovers.

videos.headline: Taylor goes untouched for 16-yard TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor bounces back after fumbling and goes 16 yards into the end zone for a Wisconsin touchdown.

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Taylor picks up 21 yards on difficult catch
videos.description: A.J. Taylor adjusts to the throw from Alex Hornibrook and makes the catch while falling to the turf.

videos.headline: Taylor breaks free for 43-yard gain
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor breaks a tackle and races 43 yards past the New Mexico defense.

videos.headline: Hornibrook connects with Taylor for 10-yard TD
videos.description: Alex  Hornibrook drops back and finds A.J. Taylor in the end zone vs. New Mexico.

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Nelson intercepts New Mexico QB
videos.description: Wisconsin freshman Scott Nelson steps in front of the errant throw by Sheriron Jones and returns it 22 yards.

videos.headline: Taylor runs for 2nd TD of game
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor powers through New Mexico defenders for his second score to put Wisconsin ahead 24-7.

videos.headline: Hornibrook completes 44-yard bomb to Taylor
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook runs the play action and finds A.J. Taylor deep down field as he goes over 100 yards receiving on the day with a 44-yard reception.

videos.headline: Jones finds Lilly for New Mexico TD
videos.description: Sheriron Jones rolls out to the right and connects with  Elijah Lilly for a 5-yard touchdown to cut into Wisconsin's lead.

videos.headline: Taylor breaks 250 yards, scores 3rd TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor sets a new career high for rushing yards in a single game as he plunges ahead for his third touchdown vs. New Mexico.

videos.headline: Cone's INT forces 3rd New Mexico turnover of 2nd half
videos.description: Madison Cone steps in front of the New Mexico receiver and intercepts Sheriron Jones' pass.

videos.headline: Wisconsin QB, WR connect for 1st TDs
videos.description: Danny Vanden Boom and Taj Mustapha get their first career touchdown pass and touchdown catch respectively on a 3-yard score.
